name: Technian #6
description:
This work explores the question of "If the technology has a face, what would it be like? what's the story behind it? "

This art piece is a compilation of the "Technian," which was composed of AI-generated "story & portrait." It conceptualizes the form of the SOTA computer graphics. Because of the randomness and the characteristics of the black box in the process of AI creation, the Technian represents the self-awareness of Technology.

This animation is fully generated by my own AI model without human manipulation.

see more details at: https://www.behance.net/gallery/123250449/AI-art-Murder-Model
